  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Data Destruction in Treasury and Risk Management</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><meta name=\"abstract\" content=\"You use data destruction objects to delete data for which the retention period has expired and there is no legal hold. You can delete data from the database by executing a data destruction run for a corresponding data destruction object.\"><meta name=\"description\" content=\"You use data destruction objects to delete data for which the retention period has expired and there is no legal hold. You can delete data from the database by executing a data destruction run for a corresponding data destruction object.\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page concept  - topic-topic concept-concept \" id=\"loio68ba813c01864e48a63f7cf353b6e2d0\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Data Destruction in Treasury and Risk Management</h1><div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You use data destruction objects to delete data for which the retention period has expired and there is no legal hold. You can delete data\nfrom the database by executing a data destruction run for a corresponding data destruction object.</p>\n<div class=\"p\">The following table shows the data destruction object available for Treasury and Risk Management:<div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" id=\"loio68ba813c01864e48a63f7cf353b6e2d0__table_slr_5yw_kfb\" class=\"table\" data-table-id=\"table_slr_5yw_kfb\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"50%\"><col width=\"50%\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\" style=\"text-align:left;\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d911188e58\"><p>Data destruction object</p></th>\n<th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d911188e61\"><p>Description of data destruction object</p></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d911188e58 \"><p>TRTM_LR_DESTRUCTION</p></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d911188e61 \"><p>Destroying Limit Reservation Data Using TRTM_LR_DESTRUCTION</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div>\n</div><div class=\"related-links\"> </div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
